Track your time use and remind yourself to meditate/pick up the rice milk.

DEPENDENCIES:
    OS: Mac OS X and growl (for notifications)
    Lang: Ruby 1.8.6 +
    Libs: Depends on the daemons gem, thought I will probably switch to daemon-kit in the future (since it's looking better every day).

USAGE: ruby surrender.rb [args]

FEATURES:
    - runs as daemon
    - Growl notifications
    
UPCOMING FEATURES:
    - client server architecture
    - simple natural language parsing for interface
    - full gem packaging
    - rdoc compat
    - saving to file system